title: Voyageurs National Park: GPS Waypoints
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Directions & Transportation     GPS Waypoints              GPS Waypoints       GPS Waypoints  This information is provided to assist in locating specific locations and is not provided for navigation. Always bring a Navigation map and know how to read it when boating in the park.  Download a GPX file of waypoints for select locations, aids to navigation, and hazards to navigation in the park. This file type is compatible with many GPS units. Download a list of GPS coordinates (PDF) of campsites, houseboat sites, and day use sites.
